t;: &quot;string&quot;,\n  &quot;approved&quot;: false,\n  &quot;feedback&quot;: &quot;string&quot;,\n  &quot;issues&quot;: &quot;value&quot;\n}\n\n\n**REQUIRED OUTPUT** — You MUST end your response with a JSON object in a code fence matching this schema:\n```json\n{\n  \"$schema\": \"https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema\",\n  \"type\": \"object\",\n  \"properties\": {\n    \"reviewer\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\"\n    },\n    \"approved\": {\n      \"type\": \"boolean\"\n    },\n    \"feedback\": {\n      \"type\": \"string\"\n    },\n    \"issues\": {\n      \"default\": [],\n      \"type\": \"array\",\n      \"items\": {\n        \"type\": \"object\",\n        \"properties\": {\n          \"severity\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\",\n            \"enum\": [\n              \"critical\",\n              \"major\",\n              \"minor\",\n              \"nit\"\n            ]\n          },\n          \"title\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          },\n          \"file\": {\n            \"default\": null,\n            \"anyOf\": [\n              {\n                \"type\": \"string\"\n              },\n              {\n                \"type\": \"null\"\n              }\n            ]\n          },\n          \"description\": {\n            \"type\": \"string\"\n          }\n        },\n        \"required\": [\n          \"severity\",\n          \"title\",\n          \"file\",\n          \"description\"\n        ],\n        \"additionalProperties\": false\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"required\": [\n    \"reviewer\",\n    \"approved\",\n    \"feedback\",\n    \"issues\"\n  ],\n  \"additionalProperties\": false\n}\n```\nOutput the JSON at the END of your response. The workflow will fail without it." agentCommand=claude
